text: Skokie School District 68 is a school district headquartered in Skokie, Illinois. It serves northwestern sections of Skokie and a portion of Morton Grove. ==Schools== ; Junior high school * Old Orchard Junior High School ; Elementary schools * Devonshire Elementary School * Highland Elementary School * Jane Stenson Elementary School ; Preschool * Early Childhood Center ==References== ==External links== * Skokie School District 68 ** District Boundary Category:School districts in Cook County, Illinois Category:Skokie, Illinois
